Class ItemMergeInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.itemhistoryservice.transport.ItemMergeInfo

  • public final class ItemMergeInfo
extends Object
    Information about an Item that has acted as the source in a merge operation, which forms part of a MergeHistory.
    Since:
    4.0
